# Launcher assets directory

Place persona portrait PNGs, intro MP3s, and music tracks here.

Structure:
  launcher-assets/
    portraits/<persona-key>.png     persona portrait (64x64 or 128x128, pixel art recommended)
    intros/<persona-key>.mp3         persona intro clip (played on selection)
    intros/<persona-key>-deploy.mp3  persona deploy confirmation clip
    music/*.mp3                       background music tracks (auto-listed on /launcher/music)

This directory is empty by default. The launcher gracefully handles missing assets.
